designs.title: SHOPEE - ECOMMERCE APP UI KIT
designs.description: Shopee is a clean, minimal design and very detailed E-commerce UI kit for iOS & Android. You can use this UI kit to create your e-commerce shop. This UI kit comes with trendy designs. The package includes 30+ Ecommerce screens and works in Adobe XD. Each screen is fully customizable, easy to use, and well-organized.
